          "Type": "System.String",
          "Value": "float3 HullFunction(float u, float v) {\n  return float3(\n    (v + 1) * 10 + sin(u),\n    (u - 0.5) + sin(u) ,\n    v + u * sin(u + v)\n  );\n}"
